I mean, the Indians community would not be

35
00:01:30,364 --> 00:01:31,705
what it is today without the internet.

36
00:01:32,752 --> 00:01:34,473
So I don't feel like I need to sell anybody

37
00:01:34,613 --> 00:01:36,914
on all of the incredible things that the internet does for us

38
00:01:37,034 --> 00:01:39,155
and how it quite literally changed the world.

39
00:01:39,775 --> 00:01:41,275
It's essential to the work that we do here

40
00:01:41,375 --> 00:01:42,436
and how we live our lives.

41
00:01:42,556 --> 00:01:45,957
So it's good, actually, most of the time.

42
00:01:47,397 --> 00:01:50,158
The thing is, we just don't have the luxury of logging off

43
