00:02:19,178 --> 00:02:21,118
So yeah, it's not that simple.

56
00:02:22,618 --> 00:02:23,939
The internet is no longer some sort

57
00:02:23,979 --> 00:02:26,359
of secret geographical place you access

58
00:02:26,399 --> 00:02:28,200
on the family desktop to look at websites

59
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:30,280
about Bigfoot on websites that have a black background

60
